                        electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged.
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="mt-8
                    py-1
                    lg:py-5"
                    >
                        <a
                            href="/pricing"
                            class="font-sans text-xs tracking-[.2em] border-black border-2 hover:bg-black hover:text-white
                        px-4
                        lg:px-12
